        "created_at": "2017-04-03T21:17:39.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The wine would have been vinified by the Hospices de Nuits and then raised and bottled by Aegerter after its purchase at auction.</p>",
        "post_number": 3,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 6,
